net.sitecore.android.sdk.api
Class ScApiSession

java.lang.Object
  net.sitecore.android.sdk.api.ScApiSession

public abstract class ScApiSession
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds information about connection properties and user authentication properties. All requests to Sitecore Item Web API are built using instances of ScApiSession.

uploadMedia

public abstract UploadMediaRequestOptions uploadMedia(java.lang.String itemPath,
                                                      java.lang.String itemName,
                                                      java.lang.String mediaFilePath)
Creates UploadMediaRequestOptions that describe image upload request. Afterwards UploadMediaService.startUpload(android.content.Context, net.sitecore.android.sdk.api.UploadMediaRequestOptions, com.android.volley.Response.Listener, com.android.volley.Response.ErrorListener) or UploadMediaService.newUploadIntent(android.content.Context, net.sitecore.android.sdk.api.UploadMediaRequestOptions, com.android.volley.Response.Listener, com.android.volley.Response.ErrorListener) must be used.

Parameters:
itemPath - Media folder path to upload media to.
itemName - Name of the media item.
mediaFilePath - any of "content://"(file name should be explicitly set), "http://", "file://"
Returns:
UploadMediaRequestOptions that describe image upload request.
